message.text:
Who runs NewsDotCOMM? These departments do. 😉

News and content are built through collaborative efforts. From production’s ideas and creatives’ visuals to the marketing’s captions, talents’ bold voices, and technicals’ smooth operations—they’ve got it all covered. 

Think you’ve got the skills to be part of this team? This is your sign to apply, you’ve got 4 hours left! 🖋️⏳

🔗: https://forms.gle/zPgVzzHEsRbwD7eB7

Caption by Elaiza Alcayde

#RoadToNDC 
#FEUNewsDotCOMM

message.text:
Hi everyone! 👋🔰

📣 Seeking Inputs for a Communication Planning Project 📣

looking for IHSN students who are (or were) part of the IHSN Student Council and familiar with how the council operates—things like document processing, event coordination, and other internal procedures.

✅ Open to current or former SC members
✅ Students from any IHSN program are welcome
(especially those in BS Nutrition and Dietetics or BS Pharmacy)

The participation is simple: a short written interview via chat or Google Docs with about 5–10 questions focused solely on the organization. 📝

All responses will remain confidential and used only for academic purposes.

If you’re willing to help, please send me a private message. Thank you so much po! ❤️💕😍
